{
  "stem": "27285.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went separately, so that-- I can remember only that we were with my mother and not with my parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very cold, and very windy, so it-- I don't know, and rainy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we've just crossed, I mean-- I don't know how we came to the border, but you went on foot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If it was planned, of course they wouldn't tell children because they might talk, so nobody talked about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So just one evening we went out and didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We left everything behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to the border, and we had to cross a lot of fields, and it was rainy and muddy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember this squishy feeling of lifting your feet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still can feel it in my body how heavy it was, because it was so full of mud, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother was so exhausted with those two kids, she said, no, I've had enough, we are going back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I started to stomp my foot, which I couldn't very well in this mud, and said, no, we went so far, we are going on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are not going back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know why I did it, I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I only know that I did, and that my mother said, yes, that's what you did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from that moment, actually, I also was responsible already for my sister because half a year later, my parents, who were united in Brno, which, you know, it's the capital of Moravia, went on to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this is a later story to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know only how my mother was-- we didn't have any relatives on the border town of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was Mikulov, or Nikolsburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
